pr_title: GUI: Add an icon grid to the launcher display
pr_body:
This is the GSoC '21 project : "GUI for Game Library Management"

The additions made by this PR are as follows -
- Add a grid view of game icons to the launcher as an alternative display to the existing list display of games (toggle-able between list and grid view). 
- Use the game icons from the https://github.com/scummvm/scummvm-icons repo and flag icons from https://flagpedia.net. 
- Clicking on a game brings up a tray of the common game-related tasks.
- Add the ability to group launcher entries, in both the list view and the grid view.
- There are several options to group the grid elements, which are formed using the metadata from the https://github.com/scummvm/scummvm-web repo, by converting the .yaml files to .xml files. 
- The groups are expandable and collapsible by clicking on the header.
- The themes have also been upgraded to support grid layout as well.

Weekly updates are tracked on the blog : https://blogs.scummvm.org/av-dx/
Summary of all the work done within GSoC '21 : https://blogs.scummvm.org/av-dx/2021/08/23/goodbye-gsoc-21-gsoc-summary/
Detailed List of the TODOs : https://blogs.scummvm.org/av-dx/2021/08/23/the-unfinished-business-todos/
Icon pack to use with the grid : https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DdJZC2SFRvmPjEtoM0-WJDkcUXH1jWx3/view?usp=sharing
(Extract the icons.zip and point the "Icon Path" setting under "Options -> Paths" to the extracted folder)

A screenshot of the grid:
![Screenshot from 2021-08-23 19-22-59](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/56360160/130459297-a018a02a-d653-4a39-8497-69231b93e040.png)

A screenshot of the new grouped list view:
![Screenshot from 2021-08-23 19-25-01](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/56360160/130459703-9edf19a9-ab0d-492c-b09d-13026817b3ee.png)
